  <section id="home">
    <h2>Home</h2>
    <p>I love video games because they help me relax, think creatively, and challenge myself. My favorite games are Roblox and Geometry Dash. Both are fun, colorful, and full of cool levels to explore or create!</p>
  </section>

  <section id="about">
    <h2>About My Favorite Games</h2>
    <h3>Roblox</h3>
    <p>Roblox is a game platform where you can play and create your own worlds. It’s full of imagination and multiplayer adventures. I enjoy playing with friends and building my own games.</p>

    <h3>Geometry Dash</h3>
    <p>Geometry Dash is a rhythm-based platformer. It’s all about timing and focus. I like trying to pass hard levels and unlock new icons.</p>

    <ul>
      <li>Roblox helps me be creative</li>
      <li>Geometry Dash improves my reflexes</li>
      <li>Both games are challenging and fun</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

